title: One year after the Google walkout, key organizers reflect on the risk to their careers
description: Claire Stapleton and Meredith Whittaker staked their careers when they organized the Google walkout in November 2018. It was a risk they felt they had to take.

title: Russia rolls out its 'sovereign internet'
description: On Friday, a controversial new law took effect in Russia: The so-called "sovereign internet" law, which mandates the creation of an independent internet for Russia.
